checklistText:
<size=21>SPS DEORBIT & ENTRY</size>
VEHICLE PREP COMPLETE
P30 - EXTERNAL ΔV
1) V37E 30E
2) F 06 33		GETI (hr, min, .01 sec)
					(ACCEPT) PRO

3) F 06 81		ΔVX, Y, Z (LV) (.1fps)

					(REJECT) V25E TO LOAD DESIRED DATA

4) F 06 42		HA, HP, ΔV (.1nm,.1nm,.1fps)
					Set ΔV counter
					(ACCEPT) PRO
					(REJECT) Reselect P30 or P27. Load new param.

5) F 16 45		M, TFI, MGA (marks, min-sec,.01°)
					*MGA -00002: If		*
					* IMU not aligned	*
				SET DET
				PRO
				F 37 00E

	MAN ATT (3) - MIN IMP
	RCS TRNFR - CM

	TEST RING 1 THRUSTERS

8) SPS THRUSTING PREP

	Load DAP
	BMAG MODE (3) - RATE 2
	SC CONT - CMC/AUTO

9) USE P52 OPTION 1 to align IMU with burn direction (Preferred)

	V49E

				PRO

13) 06 18		AUTO MNVR TO FDAI RPY ANGLES (.01°)

14) F 50 18		REQUEST TRIM MNVR TO FDAI RPY ANGLES
				ALIGN S/C ROLL (.01°)
				GDC ALIGN

TVC CHECK & PREP
	[P08] cb STAB CONT SYS (all) - close
	cb SPS (12) - close
	Set ΔVC (verify)
	EMS FUNC - ΔV (verify)
	MAN ATT (3) - RATE CMD
	ATT DB - MIN

	SCS TVC (2) - RATE CMD
	ΔV CG - CSM

+54:00m (-6:00)

	TVC SERVO PWR #1 - AC1/MNA
	TVC SERVO PWR #2 - AC2/MNB
	ROT CONT PWR NORMAL (2) - AC
	ROT CONT PWR DIRECT (2) - OFF

+54:00m (-6:00)

	PRIMARY TVC CHECK
	GMBL MOT P1-Y1 - START/ON

	Verify MTVC
   		*IF SCS: SCS TVC (2) - AUTO	*
	SC CONT - CMC (SCS)

	ENTR

					(ACCEPT) SC CONT - CMC (verify)
				PRO

				Monitor GPI Response:
					00,02,-02,00,02,-02,00, Trim
						*TEST FAIL: 			*

						*KEY REL TO 16				*

				RATE - HIGH

59:55 (-00:05)

F 99 40		ENG ON ENABLE REQUEST
				(AUTO IGN)            PRO AT TFI > 0 Sec
				(BYPASS IGN)         ENTR to 19 (prfrm switching in 18)
				(EXIT) V37E 00E
				
17) 00:00		IGN		*IF SCS: THRUST PB - PUSH*

	06 40	TFC, VG,  ΔVM (min-sec,.1fps,.1fps)
				*F 97 40 SPS Thrsut fail 	*
				*ΔV THRUST B(A) - NORMAL	*
				*(RESTART) PRO to IGN		*
				*(RECYCLE) ENTR to TIG-05sec	*
	
			SPS THRUST lt - ON
			ΔV THRUST B(A) - NORMAL
				*IF SCS: +X & THRUST PB - PUSH*
	
MONITOR THRUSTING
	Pc 95-105 psia
	EMS COUNTING DOWN
	SPS INJ VLVS (4) - OPEN
	SPS He vlvs tb-gray
	SPS FUEL/OXID PRESS - 170-195 psia
	PUGS - BALANCED

00:XX		ECO

18) F 16 40		TFC (STATIC), VG, ΔVM (min-sec,.1fps)
					ΔV THRUST A&B - OFF
				VERIFY THRUST OFF
					SPS INJ VLVS (4) - CLOSED
					SPS He vlvs tb (2) - bp
					GMBL MTRS (4) - OFF
					TVC SERVO PWR 1&2 - OFF
				PRO
19) F 16 85		VG XYZ (CM) (.1fps)
					NULL RESIDUALS
					RECORD ΔV COUNTER & RESIDUALS
					EMS FUNC - OFF
					EMS MODE -STBY
					TRANS CONT PWR - PFF
					BMAG MODE (3) - RATE 2
					cb DIRECT ULLATE (2) - open
					cb SPS P&Y (4) - open
					TAPE RCDR - off (ctr)
				PRO

20) F 37 V82E

21) F 16 44		HA, HP, TFF (.1nm,min-sec)
					PRO

22) F 37 00E

23) When COMP ACTY lt out: V66E

24) MNVR TO CM/SM ATT
	SC CONT - SCS
	YAW right 45° from Burn Att (315°)
	BMAG MODE (3) -ATT 1/RATE 2

Getting the Entry PAD:
1) Use CREW MEMBERS -> REQUEST PADS & CHARTS -> OPEN ENTRY PAD FORM to open the Entry PAD.
2) Use CREW MEMBERS -> REQUEST PADS & CHARTS -> REQUEST ENTRY PAD to get the Entry PAD data.
3) Fill in the Entry Pad, from top to bottom.
4) Use Program 52, Option 2 (Nominal REFSMMAT) to align IMU with the RRT parameter from the PAD.
5) Align the GDC to the new IMU orientation
6) Use V49E to start to maneuver to Entry Attitude (0, 168/209, 0)

25) PWR REDUCT
	HI GAIN ANT PWR - OFF
	FC PUMPS (3) - OFF
	FC 2 MNA - OFF
	Verify loads balanced
	VHF AM (A&B) - off (ctr)
	[P05] cb ECS RAD CONT/HTR (2) - open
	cb RAD HTRS OVLD (2) - open
	cb WASTE H2O/URINE DUMP HTRS (2) - open
	POT H2O HTR - OFF
	GLY EVAP TEMP IN - MAN

26) P61 - ENTRY PREP
	V37E 61E

27) F 06 61		IMPACT LAT, LONG, HDS UP/DN (.01° ,.01° ,+/-00001)
					V25E TO CHANGE
					(ACCEPT) PRO

28) F 06 60		GMAX, V400K,GAMMA EI (.01G, fps,.01°)
				(PRO)

29) F 06 63		RTOGO (.1nm)
				VIO (fps)
				TFE (min-sec)
				(ACCEPT) PRO
				
P62 - CM/SM SEP & PRE-ENTRY MNVR
30) F 50 25		00041 REQUEST CM/SM SEP
					PRIM GLY to RAD - BYPASS (verify)
					EMS MODE - STBY (verify)
					CM RCS LOGIC - on (up)
					SECS LOGIC (2) - on (up) (verify)
					SECS PYRO ARM (2) - ARM
					C&WS - CM
					CM/SM SEP (2) - on (up)
						If docking ring still on:
							CSM/LM FNL SEP (2) - on(up)(verify)
					MAN ATT(3) - MIN IMP
					BMAG MODE(3) - RATE 2
					C&W MODE - CM
					RCS TRNFR - CM
					CM RCS PRPLNT 1&2 - up (verify)
					CM RCS PRPLNT 1&2 tb (2) - gray (verify)
					CM RCS MANF PRESS - 287-302 psia
					CM RCS LOGIC - OFF
					SECS PYRO ARM (2) - SAFE
					Monitor V MNA/B:
						*If <25vdc go to EMERG POWER DOWN*
				
					YAW back to 0°
					MNVR to ENTRY ATT
						R 0°  (Lift UP)
						P Horiz on 29°  mark (400K)
						Y 0° 
					MAINTAIN HORIZ TRACK
				PRO (Act ENTRY DAP Att Hold)

31) F 06 61		IMPACT LAT, LONG, HDS/DN (.01°,.01°,-00001)
			
				EMS INITIALIZATION
						*If scroll not on 37K	*
						* EMS FUNC - TEST 5		*
						* Slew scroll to 37K		*
					EMS FUNC - RNG SET
					Set RNG TO PAD DATA RNG
					EMS FUNC - V0 SET
					Slew scroll to PAD DATA VIO
					EMS MODE - STBY (verify)
					EMS FUNC - ENTRY
				
				RSI ALIGNMENT
					RSI is automatically aligned in Reentry.
					Ensure IMU is aligned and GDC is aligned to IMU.

				PRO (CMC Guidance)

32) POSS 06 22	FINAL ATT DISP, RPY (.01°)

P63 - ENTRY INIT
33) 06 64		G,VI,RTOGO (.01,fps,.01nm)
					FDAI SCALE - 5/5
					ROT CONTR PWR DIR (2)-MNA/MNB(verify)
					TAPE RCDR - HBR/RCD/FWD/CMC RESET
					HORIZ CK
					Pitch error needle goes toward zero
						approaching .05G time.

P64 - ENTRY POST .05G
34) 06 74		BETA, VI, G (.01°,fps,.01G)
					RTOGO AT .05G AGREES WITH EMS-verify
					HORIZ CK
				
					At .05 G time:
						EMS MODE - BACKUP/VHF RNG
					.05 G Lt - on
				
					If CMC is GO:
						MAN ATT (3) - RATE CMD
						SC CONT - CMC
					.05 G sw - on(up)
					EMS ROLL - on(up)
					NOTE: To monitor N68, Key V16 N68E
					Compare RSI & FDAI
					EMS GO/NO GO
						G-V Plot within limits
					
P67 - ENTRY - FINAL PHASE (0.2G)
35) 06 66		BETA,CRSRNG ERR,DNRNG ERR (.01°,.1nm,.1nm)
				Relative velocity reaches 1000 ft/s
					V16N67 automatically starts
					
36) 16 67		RTOGO,LAT,LONG (Vrel=1000fps) (.1nm,.01°,.01°)
					SC CONT - SCS
					RTOGO NEG - LIFT UP
					RTOGO POS - LIFT DOWN
					Monitor altimeter
					10K
					EMS MODE - STBY
					EMS FUNC - OFF

Steps.Text: *No Deorbit burn planned? Prepare a burn using the Maneuver Planner, target entry angle of 2°*
N33 - TIG (ACCEPT: PRO, REJECT V25 then PRO)
N81 - ΔV (ACCEPT: PRO, REJECT V25 then PRO)
N42 - HA, HP, ΔV (.1nm, .1nm, .1fps) (ACCPET: PRO, V37E00E REJECT)
Use Program 52, option 1 (Preferred REFSMMAT) to align IMU with burn direction.
F 50 N18 - REQUEST MNVR TO FDAI RPY ANGLES
N18 - AUTO MNVR TO FDAI RPY ANGLES, PRO when complete
N18 - REQUEST TRIM MNVR TO FDAI RPY ANGLES
TIG-3 min - HORIZ CHK - Horiz on 3° window mk (hds up, not visible)
-00:05: PRO to accept F99 40 (ENG ON REQUEST)
Use CREW MEMBERS -> REQUEST PADS & CHARTS -> REQUEST ENTRY PAD and write down the parameters.
Use Program 52, Option 2 to align IMU to EI LVLH using RRT timestamp from PAD
GDC ALIGN to new IMU orientation
Use V49E to start to maneuver to Entry Attitude (0, 168/209, 0)
N61 - IMPACT Lat, Long, Hds Up/Dn (.01°, .01°, +/-00001): PRO
N60 - GMAX, V400K, GAMMA EI (.01G, fps, .01°) PRO
Auto tranistion from P61 to P62
MNVR to ENTRY ATT R=0° (lift up), P=Horiz on 29° mark (400K), Y=0°
Slew scroll to EI V0 (25500 for Earth Entry)
HORIZ CK - MNVR as needed (V16 to mon G load)
MNVR during entry, monitor Altimeter. When < 50K:
